<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">
  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFrameworks>net8.0;net10.0</TargetFrameworks>
    <ImplicitUsings>enable</ImplicitUsings>
    <Nullable>enable</Nullable>
    <PackageId>FluxFlow.Components.Sessions</PackageId>
    <AssemblyName>FluxFlow.Components.Sessions</AssemblyName>
    <RootNamespace>FluxFlow.Components.Sessions</RootNamespace>
    <Version>2.0.0</Version>
    <Authors>FluxFlow contributors</Authors>
    <Description>Standalone session recording, replay, and query nodes for FluxFlow: a recorder (input -> stored record), a replay source (stored records out), and a query node (request -> result + session metadata) over a host-provided ISessionStore, with broadcast output/error/event ports. No engine required.</Description>
    <PackageTags>workflow;dataflow;components;sessions;recording;replay</PackageTags>
    <PackageLicenseExpression>MIT</PackageLicenseExpression>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>Rebuilt as three standalone nodes over an injected ISessionStore and TimeProvider: SessionRecorderNode (FlowNode, input -> record), SessionReplayNode (FlowSource, stored records out), and SessionQueryNode (FlowNode, request -> result with an extra Sessions output). Every message is a FlowMessage&lt;T&gt; envelope carrying the correlation id; failures surface on the broadcast Errors port and diagnostics on Events. The node factory, component module, registration extensions, port/type constants, NodeDefinition options reader, and design-metadata provider are removed — construct a node directly and LinkTo the next one. The nodes depend only on FluxFlow.Nodes and run without the engine.</PackageReleaseNotes>
    <RepositoryType>git</RepositoryType>
    <PackageReadmeFile>README.md</PackageReadmeFile>
    <IncludeSymbols>true</IncludeSymbols>
    <SymbolPackageFormat>snupkg</SymbolPackageFormat>
  </PropertyGroup>
  <ItemGroup>
    <ProjectReference Include="..\FluxFlow.Nodes\FluxFlow.Nodes.csproj" />
  </ItemGroup>
  <ItemGroup>
    <PackageReference Include="System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow" Version="9.0.4" NoWarn="NU1510" />
  </ItemGroup>
  <ItemGroup>
    <None Include="README.md" Pack="true" PackagePath="\" />
  </ItemGroup>
</Project>
